<br>
By default, my standard twist is: Charisma, PoV &amp; Warmarch.  PoV is not there for DS.  Many mobs proc &amp; cast AE's.   The additional resists help significantly.<br>
<br>
Niv's is a great song.  The downside is the magic absorbing rune.  So, any (mob) proc or AE will nulify the song.  That's why I replace it with warmarch unless it's a mob we have very much diffculty with.<br>
<br>
Pre-time, does AC really help that much?  I read that AC vs Damage was a step function.  Going from 1800 to 1900 AC isn't going to push you to the next step.  IIRC, breaking 2100, though, will. <p><center>
