<br>
It's all conditional.  Every encounter is unique and you have to find the songs that fit your guild/group/style.<br>
<br>
For Quarm, in MA group, I play PoV, Purifying Chorus &amp; Chorus of Marr while twisting drums and lute.  I stand directly under Quarm.  The other (melee) bard(s) sing their own PoV + WoZ + Overhaste.<br>
<br>
In general we usually have at least 3 bards for quarm, though, we've done her with 2.  In that case, the non-MA bard was in cleric/caster resists group. <p><center>
