<br>
Damage shields do massive amounts of damage to time mobs contrary to what the newb bard stated above.  My ds dps on rallos in time is always in excess of 225 obviously while tanking.  Multiply this by 10 minutes which is the average rallos fight and you are doing 135k damage just from damage shield.  These mobs hit fast but not all that hard until you hit quarm is is the exact opposite.  Damage shield reduces the duration of a fight significantly in many instances such as rallos and innoruk in time, also against xegony in air.  <br>
None of the bards in my guild need to amp anymore as they are capped with AA and mods.  So they twist Veeshan, mastruq, nivs, guardian rhythms.  The importants of ac in god is immense when you are fighting a mob thats quad 2500+ while in defensive. <br>
As for cha song, i havent had DI fail in probably 4 months and i have 240ish cha unbuffed.  I used to buff cha before they added it to time gear, but since i havent had it fail in forever i dont even bother buffing or having song played.  Its fairly safe to say end game cha song in mt group is marginal at best, if not completely useless. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p201.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aflat>Aflat</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Minstrel</span><br>  Posts: 524<br> <font color=#330000>(6/30/04 1:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19552.topic&index=29>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Damage shields do massive amounts of damage to time mobs contrary to what the newb bard stated above. My ds dps on rallos in time is always in excess of 225 obviously while tanking. Multiply this by 10 minutes which is the average rallos fight and you are doing 135k damage just from damage shield. These mobs hit fast but not all that hard until you hit quarm is is the exact opposite. Damage shield reduces the duration of a fight significantly in many instances such as rallos and innoruk in time, also against xegony in air.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--> <br>
